column2: On that, I am deciding this case considering the facts, documents and the arguments
and  the  Written  Submissions  in  favour  of  the  Petitioner  and  I  grant  Writ  of  Quo
Warranto prayed for in the prayer ‘c’ and ‘d’ of the Petition dated 14th November 2022.
I fix tax cost against the 1st Respondent to be payable to the Petitioner.
Judge of the Court of Appeal
